I"Î<h4 id="situation">Situation</h4>
<ul>
  <li>The largest customer for the client had shifted procurement strategies and launched a procurement process to select a sole vendor for the next 10 years of work, at current run rates nearly $13B in value</li>
  <li>The client was struggling to reconcile the lower cost requirements needed to be competitive in the bid with the profitability the project would produce</li>
  <li>A lack of ability to view various scenarios and the sensitivity of financial outcomes to key drivers had caused their process to stall</li>
  <li>SLKone was engaged to build a more flexible project financial model that incorporated key profitability drivers as well as award scenarios</li>
